@verbatim
  \part[<<short title>>]{<<title>>}
  \chapter[<<short title>>]{<<title>>}
  \section[<<short title>>]{<<title>>}
  \paragraph[<<short title>>]{<<title>>}
  \subparagraph[<<short title>>]{<<title>>}
@end verbatim


Note:@enumerate
@item @code{\parahraph} is like an unnumbered @code{\subsubsubsections}. 
@item arguments to the above are moving arguments
@item @code{<short title>} is used in the TOC and page header
@end enumerate

For consistency of font styles for sectioning headers, use:@*
@code{\addtokomafont@{<sectioning type>@}@{<commands>@}}.@*
@code{\addtokomafont@{section@}@{\rmfamily\bfseries@}} (example)

KOMA-Script @code{\minisec@{<heading>@}} provides an unnumbered independent heading.

